response.overview: Concert of the band Psí vojáci from June 19, 1991 in Chmelnice, broadcast live by Czechoslovak Television. One of the most lively recorded concerts of this band, consisting of Filip Topol - piano, vocals, David Skála - drums, Jan Hazuka - bass guitar, Jiří Jelínek - alto saxophone. The concert took place in the Prague Junior Club Na Chmelnici, the home venue of this band.
response.title: Chmelnice 1991: Psí Vojáci na Chmelnici
